  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dba\u0daf\u0db8\u0dca  \u0d9a\u0db4\u0db1 \u0da0\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dda\u0d9b\u0dba \u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Here is the cost cutting circular",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Treasury Secretary KA Mahinda Siriwardena has issued a circular that public expenditure is used only for the most essential services."
      ],
